一共 4 种排列方式，横向左到右(默认)，横向右到左，竖向上到下(默认)，竖向下到上

item 横向排列
http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/mmdjMO

  flex-row
  items 从左向右排列，可以和 break point 结合
    <div class="d-flex flex-row">
    .flex-row
    .flex-sm-row
    .flex-md-row
    .flex-lg-row
    .flex-xl-row

  flex-row-reverse
  items 从右到左排列，可以和 break point 结合
    <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse">
    .flex-row-reverse
    .flex-sm-row-reverse
    .flex-md-row-reverse
    .flex-lg-row-reverse
    .flex-xl-row-reverse

items 竖向排列
http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/mmdjpR
  flex-column
  items 从上向下排列，可以和 break point 结合
    <div class="d-flex flex-column">
    .flex-column
    .flex-sm-column
    .flex-md-column
    .flex-lg-column
    .flex-xl-column

  flex-column-reverse
  items 从下向上排列，可以和 break point 结合
    <div class="d-flex flex-column-reverse">
    .flex-column-reverse
    .flex-sm-column-reverse
    .flex-md-column-reverse
    .flex-lg-column-reverse
    .flex-xl-column-reverse
